R 
========================================================

- Is an interpreted language and can be accessed through a command-line interpreter
- Is at its heart, a functional programming language
- A powerful program for data management and plotting
- Can be extended through user-created packages
- Can be combined with C, C++, Python etc.
- Can be used to create reports that support the idea of reproducible research
- Is free
- Works on all OS platforms



